. Cameron (editors), ''The Love That Never Ends: A Key to the Catechism of the Catholic Church'', p. 45).] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FwP7UTl2zWoC&pg=PA45&dq=catholic+hell+suffering&hl=en&ei=DtdATrvaD86WhQfR3f2_CQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCsQ6AEwADgo#v=onepage&q=catholic%20hell%20suffering&f=false |date=20170319022829 }}</ref>

